---
title: Design Tokens
description: These custom properties thread through all of Web Awesome's components, giving things a consistent look and feel.
layout: docs
override:tags: []
---

<p>
{% markdown %}
  {{ description }}
{% endmarkdown %}
</p>

<div class="search-list modern-card-list">
  <section class="search-list-grid">
    {% for page in collections.tokens | sort(false, false, 'data.title') %}
      <a href="{{ page.url }}">
        <wa-card>
          <span class="page-name">{{ page.data.title }}</span>
          {% if page.data.description %}
            <p class="modern-card-summary">{{ page.data.description | inlineMarkdown | striptags | safe }}</p>
          {% endif %}
        </wa-card>
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </section>
  <div class="search-list-empty" hidden>
    No results found
  </div>
</div>
